nodes.text: Iakar was a jungle planet and the homeworld of the Iakaru species located in the Iakar system. During the Clone Wars companies such as the Chiewab, Fabreth Medical, and Merisee Prime set up research installations on the planet which drove the Iakaru deeper into the jungle. Six months before the Battle of Scarif, a Rebel Alliance Special Forces team stole medical supplies from Iakar.
